{"title":"原子能两首","authors":["方纪"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":1,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"原子能两首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"方纪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回旋加速器"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回旋加速器，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不停地旋转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从右向左，向左，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每秒钟百千万次。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"加速回旋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是为了增加热力；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回旋呵回旋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让物质增加热力。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让物质增加热力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放物质的能力。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像古代人钻木取火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又用火铸成锄犁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原子解放能的千分之一，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"氢解放能的百分之一，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"假如两个氢相撞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放能的十分之一。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是呵，在能的范畴里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十进位的概念不适用；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"数学是形式逻辑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"计算能力要用天文数字。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热成为能，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能成为动力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"动是生命的源泉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是宇宙的规律。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一切物质存在的形式。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"物质，不朽不灭；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能力，无穷无尽；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"运动，不休不止。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回旋加速器，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不停地旋转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从右向左，向左，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每秒钟百千万次。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原子反应堆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一座谷仓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一座碉堡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蕴藏着无限的能量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掩蔽着猛烈的火力。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铀棒，只像是一束筷子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深藏在圆柱形的水泥体中；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而透过那一座座试验孔道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正发生出神妙的奇迹："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同位素被送往医疗机构，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"核反应在揭开物质秘密；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿白衣的研究人员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"温静得像善心的护士一样；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但他们守护的不是病人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一个力大无穷的大力士！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它能翻山倒海，升天入地；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今乖乖地听从人的支配。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要它为人类造福，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为和平事业服务，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发掘宇宙间一切资源，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来建设社会主义。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原子反应堆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的原子反应堆！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的成就和骄傲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的光荣和胜利。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来，跨进原子时代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛驴为我们服务得太久了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让科学插上幻想的翅膀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乘东风高高飞去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一座谷仓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一座碉堡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蕴藏着无限的能量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掩蔽着猛烈的火力。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一月十九日·北京）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}